This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: guelph humber
des: Guelph-Humber Alexa skill provides instant answers to more than 100 questions specific to the ACTS department at University of Guelph-Humber, from "How to use Guelph-Humber email?" to "What are the University hours?". Alexa will also be able to provide information about Wi-Fi, printing, and cloud services, among many other aspects of Academic and Campus Technology Services.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
